blacklist(address).details: Blacklists a user by address, preventing them from interacting with certain functions.Emits a {UserBlackListed} event upon successful blacklisting.

params.user: The address of the user to blacklist.

constructor.details: Constructor that initializes the contract with a name and symbol for the NFT collection.

getTokenUri(uint256).details: Returns the URI associated with a given token ID.

params.tokenId: The ID of the token whose URI is being queried.

isAddressBlackListed(address).details: Checks if an address is blacklisted.

returns._0: True if the address is blacklisted otherwise false.

isRegistered(address).details: Checks if a address is registered.

returns._0: True if the address is registered otherwise false.

mintNft(address,bytes32).details: Allows a user to mint a new NFT.The `s_tokenCounter` is incremented using an unchecked block to save gas, as it will not exceed its limit.Emits an {NftMinted} event upon successful minting.

params.recipient: The address to receive the minted NFT.
params.tokenUri: The URI associated with the newly minted NFT.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

register(address).details: Allows a user to register with the contract by paying the registration fee.Emits a {UserRegistered} event upon successful registration.

params.user: The address of the user to register.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby disabling any functionality that is only available to the owner.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

blacklist(address).notice: This function can only be called by the contract owner.

mintNft(address,bytes32).notice: The caller must not be blacklisted, must be registered, and must send the exact minting fee.

register(address).notice: The caller must not be blacklisted and must send the exact registration fee.
